		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Yuki-onna</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:229px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Yukionna.jpg" class="image" title="A Yuki-onna"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/95/Yukionna.jpg" width="227" height="736" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Yukionna.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
A <b>Yuki-onna</b></div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Yuki-onna</b> <span style="font-weight: normal">(<span class="t_nihongo_kanji"><span lang="ja" xml:lang="ja">雪女</span></span> <span class="t_nihongo_help noprint"><sup><a href="/wiki/Help:Japanese" title="Help:Japanese"><span class="t_nihongo_icon" style="color: #00e; font: bold 80% sans-serif; text-decoration: none; padding: 0 .1em;">?</span></a></sup></span>, snow woman)</span> is a <a href="/wiki/Spiritual_being" title="Spiritual being" class="mw-redirect">spirit</a> or <a href="/wiki/Y%C5%8Dkai" title="Yōkai">yōkai</a> found in <a href="/wiki/Japanese_folklore" title="Japanese folklore">Japanese folklore</a>. She is a popular figure in <a href="/wiki/Japanese_animation" title="Japanese animation" class="mw-redirect">Japanese animation</a>, <a href="/wiki/Manga" title="Manga">manga</a> and <a href="/wiki/Japanese_literature" title="Japanese literature">literature</a>. Yuki-onna is sometimes confused with <a href="/wiki/Yama-uba" title="Yama-uba">Yama-uba</a> ("mountain <a href="/wiki/Crone" title="Crone">crone</a>"), but the two figures are not the same.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="clear: left; margin-bottom: .5em; float: left; padding: .5em 1.4em .8em 0; background: none; width: auto;">
<tr>
